languages.en: //(0,3.150982)\\Hm, Vanya Shah is eager to meet the new foreman//(3.150982,5.11289)\\of the Mumbai Laundry business.//(5.11289,8.289328)\\However, the foreman has taken refuge in his office,//(8.289328,10.88411)\\unwilling to meet with her at this time.//(10.88411,13.28211)\\You might be able to use this to your advantage, 47.
languages.fr: //(0,2.446687)\\Hmm, Vanya Shah a hâte de rencontrer//(2.446687,5.137845)\\le nouveau contremaître du lavoir de Bombay.//(5.137845,8.454045)\\Celui-ci s'est cependant réfugié dans son bureau//(8.454045,11.00438)\\et refuse de la voir.//(11.00438,15.00438)\\Vous pourriez utiliser ceci à votre avantage, 47.
